window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>4 volumes in a single offering!</b></p> <p>David always was an outdoorsman and an explorer. But when Earth merged with the magical world of Tannoris, it suddenly became too dangerous for anyone without a Class to leave the cities. A shame, too, because with elves, foxkin, catkin, and many other magical beings abound, there is plenty for him to experience!</p> <p>But now, David’s dream just might come true! A mystical ritual will awaken his Class, and a budding homestead on the wild frontier is waiting for him to take ownership.</p> <p>He won’t be going alone, though—a charming fox girl will teach him the ways of the frontier. And in return, David might teach her some things, too.</p>"; 
